bc9c208e-93a8-4e39-93d0-305870028a61.title: Cover Fire
bc9c208e-93a8-4e39-93d0-305870028a61.summary: In Cover Fire you received the call for duty to be the shooter who lead a squad of veterans through sieged cities, deserts and fields taken by guerrillas, and defeat all kind of enemies in the war with the biggest graphic, greatest arsenal and the best offline gameplay on mobile.

dbc76b6e-f3cf-4006-a8a5-4a632a1634f9.title: Zombieland
dbc76b6e-f3cf-4006-a8a5-4a632a1634f9.summary: Zombieland: Double Tap- Road Trip is a ridiculously fun top-down twin-stick shooter featuring local co-op multiplayer for up to four players.

fc1cce6f-8e71-4961-b0e4-ae8c0b93f782.title: Eve Online
fc1cce6f-8e71-4961-b0e4-ae8c0b93f782.summary: EVE Online is a free-to-play community driven space MMO where players can choose their own path from countless different options. Experience space exploration, immense PvP and PvE battles, mining, industry and a thriving player economy in an ever-expanding sandbox.
